=== Etymology ===
Word is mashup by australian philosopher and researcher Glenn Albrecht of the roots {{L.}} ''[[solacium|sōlācium]]'' ([[solace|comfort]]) and {{AGr.}} [[-algia|algia]] (pain), which together aptly conjure the word [[nostalgia]].

